        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-1d04e199-37c8-43e7-b36c-a71d0899f01a">
                Brigadier Head
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1d04e199-37c8-43e7-b36c-a71d0899f01a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-04-20/debates/0dba6665-daf9-44e6-9f09-975119a9ad2e/WesternUnion(CouncilMeeting)#contribution-1d04e199-37c8-43e7-b36c-a71d0899f01a">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Will the Minister of Defence bear in mind that we shall never make a reality of Western defence just through plans or production or even <span id="330" class="column-number" data-column-number="330"></span> " infrastructural" defence, but that we shall only do so by the creation of well-prepared and up-to-date defence forces; and will he devote his own mind and that of our Allies to that as a matter of urgency?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1d04e199-37c8-43e7-b36c-a71d0899f01a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-04-20/debates/0dba6665-daf9-44e6-9f09-975119a9ad2e/WesternUnion(CouncilMeeting)#contribution-1d04e199-37c8-43e7-b36c-a71d0899f01a">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
